        +cdc-text._deco.__describe.js-sr_1 The main task of landing page is to familiarize potential investors with ICO and to inform them about important features of the new project.
        +cdc-text._gray._proxima._tar._md-fz10.__caption.js-sr_2 First Screen
    block

